#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/deform/smooth.rst:4
msgid "Smooth Modifier"
msgstr "平滑修改器--knight翻译"

#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/deform/smooth.rst:8
msgid "Smooth modifier applied to a subdivided cube"
msgstr "对细分后的立方体使用平滑修改器"

#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/deform/smooth.rst:11
msgid ""
"This modifier smooths a mesh by flattening the angles between adjacent faces"
" in it, just like :menuselection:`Specials --> Smooth` in Edit Mode. It "
"smooths without subdividing the mesh - the number of vertices remains the "
"same."
msgstr ""
"该修改器通过压平相邻面的角度来平滑网格，就像编辑模式下的 :menuselection:`特殊操作--> 平滑` "
"。该操作不会细分网格——顶点的数目保持不变。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/deform/smooth.rst:15
msgid ""
"This modifier is not limited to smoothing, though. Its control factor can be"
" configured outside the ``0.0 - 1.0`` range (including negative values), "
"which can result in interesting deformations."
msgstr "然而该修改器不限于平滑。其控制因子可以配置在 ``0.0 - 1.0`` 范围之外（包括负值），这样可能产生有趣的形变效果。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/deform/smooth.rst:21
msgid "Options"
msgstr "选项"

#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/deform/smooth.rst:23
msgid "X, Y, Z"
msgstr "X、Y、Z轴"

#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/deform/smooth.rst:24
msgid ""
"Toggle buttons to enable/disable the modifier in the X, Y and/or Z axes "
"directions."
msgstr "开启或关闭修改器在X、Y、Z轴方向上的应用。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/deform/smooth.rst:27
msgid "Factor"
msgstr "因子"

#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/deform/smooth.rst:26
msgid ""
"The factor to control the smoothing amount. Higher values will increase the "
"effect. Values outside this range (above ``1.0`` or below ``0.0``) distort "
"the mesh."
msgstr "控制平滑量的因子。值越大效果越明显，在此范围（高于 ``1.0`` 或低于 ``0.0``) 之外的值会扭曲网格。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/deform/smooth.rst:30
msgid "Repeat"
msgstr "重复"

# fbee955d2f544132910628cb77123df6
#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/deform/smooth.rst:30
msgid ""
"The number of smoothing iterations, equivalent to executing the smooth tool "
"multiple times."
msgstr ""
"平滑的迭代次数，等同于按 "
":doc:`平滑</modeling/meshes/editing/deforming/introduction#smooth>` 按钮的次数。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/deform/smooth.rst:35
msgid "Vertex Group"
msgstr "顶点组"

#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/deform/smooth.rst:33
msgid ""
"A vertex group name, to restrict the effect to the vertices in it only. This"
" allows for selective, real-time smoothing, by painting vertex weights."
msgstr "顶点组名，用来限制仅对一组顶点起效。通过绘制顶点权重达到选择性的、实时的平滑或增强效果。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/deform/smooth.rst:38
msgid "Algorithm"
msgstr "算法"

#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/deform/smooth.rst:40
msgid ""
"The calculation done by the Smooth Modifier is a simple and logical one, and"
" can be thought of as the geometric equivalent of blurring images."
msgstr "平滑修改器所做的计算逻辑很简单，可以想象成对图像模糊的几何体版本。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/deform/smooth.rst:43
msgid ""
"Each new vertex position is simply the average position of surrounding "
"vertices (the vertices connected to the same edge as it)."
msgstr "每个新的顶点位置只是相邻顶点（通过边相连的顶点）位置的平均值。"

